Class Exchange

Class Exchange 

java.lang.Object
   |
   +----Exchange
class Exchange
extends Object
This class defines the structure of a sub-pop exchange. It contains fields for the following lil-gp parameters:
  • exch[#].from
  • exch[#].fromselect
  • exch[#].to
  • exch[#].toselect
  • exch[#].count

It also stores the key value used when these objects are hashed.
